Generate ONLY the study material parts in clean Markdown. Do NOT include Flashcards or MCQs yet.

Parts to generate: Concept Explanation, Key Concepts/Rules, Shortcuts and Tricks, Solved Examples (5), Common Mistakes (at least 8), Memory Techniques/Mnemonics.

